{
  "text": "Once the original LSMOP is reformulated, the proposed LSMOF is expected to perform single-objective optimization of the weight variables in the reconstructed decision space and the reduced objective space. For simplicity, we adopt the widely used DE [CITATION_1] as the single-objective optimizers t \u2190 t + |A| /*|A| denotes the element size of A*/ 6: for r \u2190 1 : g do 7: for i \u2190 1 : NI do ",
